snippet.title: Evercade Namco Collection 1 Cartridge Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit: http://evercade.co.uk/namco-collection-1-cartridge/

The Namco Collection 1 cartridge brings 11 classic games to the Evercade, including: Pac Man, Galaxian, Dig Dug, Xevious, Battle Cars and more! The cartridge will be supplied in a stunning collectable physical case with full colour manual!

Full games list:

Pac Man

Galaxian

Dig Dug

Xevious

Star Luster

Libble Rabble

Mappy

Battle Cars

Metal Marines

Quad Challenge

Mappy Kids

GALAXIAN™, PAC-MAN™, XEVIOUS™, MAPPY™, DIG DUG™, STAR LUSTER™, Libble Rabble™, QUAD CHALLENGE™, METAL MARINES™, MAPPY KIDS™&
©BANDAI NAMCO Entertainment Inc.

BATTLE CARS™&©BANDAI NAMCO Entertainment America Inc.
